These scripts find occurrences of PR/955231. When the defect occurs, the weight
of the primary path gets stuck at 65535. Both the op and event versions of this
script report when the defect is present. 

The event script automatically adds the event options configuration although it
is not visible when viewing the config. Use 'show event-options event-scripts policies'
to see what was added by the event script.

The dampening time is set to ten minutes. Change the $DAMPEN_TIME variable to adjust this
value.

This script borrows heavily from Todd Walker's PFE_MON script.

Jeff Loughridge
jloughridge@juniper.net
